Class TrafficController

  • java.lang.Object
    • server.TrafficController

  • public class TrafficController
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the main controller of the program. Which means all the major threads are started here. The program is initiated from this clas's start method. Created by Baljit Singh Sarai on 25.02.16.
